name: 5 Beds 3.5 Baths 5,434 Sq. Ft.
description: Beautifully updated home in a lovely neighborhood. Impressive entry is flanked by formals w 12' ceilings, crown molding & stunning wood look flooring. Kitchen features an island, granite counters, white cabinetry & a large breakfast area. Inviting main living area w cathedral ceilings, fp & built-ins. French doors lead to a wonderful tiled transition room ideal for entertaining. First floor primary suite features a bay window overlooking the pool, a luxurious bath and HUGE walk-in closet. Guest bdrm and full bath also down. Grand staircase & catwalk leads to upstairs living area, 2 additional bdrms & full bath. Manicured landscaping, covered patio & sparkling pool provide an idyllic retreat. 3D tour online.
